title: Cbeebies - Christmas Edition 2008
description:
This is the updated Christmas Edition of Cbeebies which i thought i update with more cbeebies songs and rename them properly and put the proper artists and add more to them so there is 57 songs altogether.

This would be great for kids for christmas or for a present or for whatever :) they will have fun dancing or singing to these songs :)

Thanks to Stealth32 for the Christmas Edition 2007 of his Cbeebies :) which i took this from but updated it to make them all right and in tracknumber order :) and added more songs to it.



This album includes some tracks from: Bob The Builder, Tweenies, Balamory, Pingu, Postman Pat, Fifi and The Flowertots, Bill & Ben and so many more :)

It also includes the new Bob The Builder Song which is called:

Bob The Builder - Big Fish, Little Fish (Cardboard Box!)
